# Templates, TIR and reactivity

AST-local template semantics and neutral HIR handoff.

## Contract

- Input: tokenized template bodies and reactive source metadata
- Output: folded strings, runtime template handoff payloads and reactive metadata
- Decides: template composition, slot routing, folding, runtime render plans, reactivity V1
- Must not decide: backend-specific template control flow, HTML assembly
- Invariant: HIR only lowers final runtime templates and never sees TIR stores

## Main paths

- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/templates/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/templates/tir/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/module_ast/finalization/`

